nancial aid programmes]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132549885.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-probing-harvard-over-financial-aid-programmes/articleshow/132549885.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-probing-harvard-over-financial-aid-programmes/articleshow/132549885.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-22T08:06:24+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132549935,imgsize-1434453.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Hacker breaches S Korean database of nearly all diplomats]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132549834.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hacker-breaches-s-korean-database-of-nearly-all-diplomats/articleshow/132549834.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hacker-breaches-s-korean-database-of-nearly-all-diplomats/articleshow/132549834.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-22T07:59:56+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132549846,imgsize-454951.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Judge approves a $1.5 billion Anthropic settlement over pirated books used to train the Claude chatbot]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132549799.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/judge-approves-a-1-5-billion-anthropic-settlement-over-pirated-books-used-to-train-the-claude-chatbot/articleshow/132549799.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.co